videos.description: Kyrie Irving gets a block and lays in a finger roll finish on one fast break, then scores on another break as he goes up for a difficult reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie finesses in 2 fast-break buckets in a row) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie finesses in 2 fast-break buckets in a row

videos.description: Kyrie Irving goes to work on his defender from the elbow and uses a turnaround fadeaway move to draw the foul and nail the shot.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie hits Kobe-like and-1 fadeaway) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie hits Kobe-like and-1 fadeaway

videos.description: Kyrie Irving dumps off a pass to DeAndre Jordan who streaks down the lane to throw down an emphatic dunk for the Nets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie sets up Jordan for big slam in the lane) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie sets up Jordan for big slam in the lane

videos.description: James Harden throws a nice pass to DeAndre Jordan who goes up on the baseline and readjusts around a defender to throw down a devastating dunk that shakes the entire basket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jordan rattles the entire basket on massive dunk) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan rattles the entire basket on massive dunk

videos.description: James Harden needed 24 points to surpass Larry Bird for 34th place in all-time scoring and he did just that, leading the Nets to a 98-93 win vs. Pistons.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden hits 3 clutch buckets and surpasses Bird in scoring) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden hits 3 clutch buckets and surpasses Bird in scoring
